# Learn It App - Project Overview

This is a mobile learning application built with Expo and React Native. It allows users to take interactive code lessons, complete quizzes, and track their learning progress.

## Main Application Structure

- [app/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/_layout.tsx) - Main app layout with authentication flow
- [app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx) - Tab navigation structure
- [app/(auth)/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(auth)/_layout.tsx) - Authentication screens layout
